Ace_Trainer_AbelDefeat:
	.string "You’re not a Trainer that can be\n"
	.string "taken lightly!$"

Ace_Trainer_AbelPostBattle:
	.string "The Pokémon you’ll meet here won’t\n"
	.string "make it easy for you to move onward.$"

Ace_Trainer_AbelIntro:
	.string "The Trainers and Pokémon that gather\n"
	.string "here aren’t pushovers.\p"
	.string "They all have tricks up their sleeves!$"

Ace_Trainer_AliciaDefeat:
	.string "That’s right. A good Trainer will win,\n"
	.string "no matter what the situation may be.$"

Ace_Trainer_AliciaPostBattle:
	.string "The Trainer’s feelings...\n"
	.string "The Pokémon’s feelings...\p"
	.string "If they are one and the same, you\n"
	.string "will never lose.$"

Ace_Trainer_AliciaIntro:
	.string "Are you feeling all run-down?\p"
	.string "But a good Trainer is one who wins no\n"
	.string "matter the situation!$"

Ace_Trainer_AllenDefeat:
	.string "I kinda deserved that, didn’t I?\n"
	.string "I gotta stop mouthing off like that...$"

Ace_Trainer_AllenPostBattle:
	.string "I’ll remember you and your shifty\n"
	.string "Pokémon, too. I’m watching you...$"

Ace_Trainer_AllenIntro:
	.string "What, were you just dawdling around\n"
	.string "hoping I’d notice you for a battle?\p"
	.string "You know you’re going to get whupped\n"
	.string "here, don’t you?$"

Ace_Trainer_AlyssaDefeat:
	.string "Aiyeeeeh!\n"
	.string "We lost!$"

Ace_Trainer_AlyssaPostBattle:
	.string "How dare you beat us!\n"
	.string "Go away! Go!$"

Ace_Trainer_AlyssaIntro:
	.string "As an Ace Trainer, I have to take\n"
	.string "battles in stride.\p"
	.string "I need to stay cool and calm whether\n"
	.string "I win or lose.$"

Ace_Trainer_AlyssaRematch:
	.string "Last time, I got a little emotional\n"
	.string "over losing...\p"
	.string "I’ll stay cool and calm today!$"

Ace_Trainer_AntonDefeat:
	.string "What’s with your toughness?!$"

Ace_Trainer_AntonPostBattle:
	.string "You’ve battled all over, you say?\n"
	.string "That makes you tough, perhaps.$"

Ace_Trainer_AntonIntro:
	.string "We spend all our time battling in the\n"
	.string "blizzards of Snowpoint City.\p"
	.string "We’ll show you how it’s toughened\n"
	.string "us up!$"

Ace_Trainer_ArthurDefeat:
	.string "This defeat has the tang of my bitter\n"
	.string "tears...$"

Ace_Trainer_ArthurPostBattle:
	.string "I’m sorry, my Pokémon team...\p"
	.string "I promise, I’ll get better at this so\n"
	.string "you can get a taste of victory!$"

Ace_Trainer_ArthurIntro:
	.string "I want my Pokémon to get a taste of\n"
	.string "the sweetness that is victory.\p"
	.string "I can’t afford to lose this one!$"

Ace_Trainer_BlakeDefeat:
	.string "But, how...?\n"
	.string "Am I weak at battling, too?$"

Ace_Trainer_BlakePostBattle:
	.string "I’d rather be asleep in the lodge’s\n"
	.string "bed...\p"
	.string "I can’t take this cold...$"

Ace_Trainer_BlakeIntro:
	.string "I’m an elite battler, but cold is\n"
	.string "my nemesis!$"

Ace_Trainer_BlakeRematch:
	.string "I’m an elite at battling, but cold is\n"
	.string "my nemesis!$"

Ace_Trainer_BrandiDefeat:
	.string "But...\n"
	.string "This isn’t possible!$"

Ace_Trainer_BrandiPostBattle:
	.string "It’s not that you’ve won.\n"
	.string "It’s just that I lost!\p"
	.string "...It’s all the same.\n"
	.string "Go, me.$"

Ace_Trainer_BrandiIntro:
	.string "I will win. I am sure of it.\n"
	.string "Therefore, you will lose!$"

Ace_Trainer_BreannaDefeat:
	.string "My focus was too narrow minded...$"

Ace_Trainer_BreannaPostBattle:
	.string "Start by becoming friendly with your\n"
	.string "Pokémon. I mean really friendly.\p"
	.string "If you do that, you’ll learn naturally\n"
	.string "how you should battle with it.$"

Ace_Trainer_BreannaIntro:
	.string "By focusing on only one type, you can\n"
	.string "really see the strengths and\p"
	.string "weaknesses of that Pokémon.$"

Ace_Trainer_BrendaDefeat:
	.string "That was good.\n"
	.string "You’ve bonded well with your Pokémon.$"

Ace_Trainer_BrendaPostBattle:
	.string "Tough Pokémon...\n"
	.string "Tough Trainers...\p"
	.string "Their strength comes from their bond.\n"
	.string "And that’s something that can be\p"
	.string "made stronger anywhere.$"

Ace_Trainer_BrendaIntro:
	.string "Tough Pokémon...\n"
	.string "Tough Trainers...\p"
	.string "You tell me, where else can I find\n"
	.string "a place as good as this to train?$"

Ace_Trainer_BrennaDefeat:
	.string "I can’t believe how tough you are!$"

Ace_Trainer_BrennaPostBattle:
	.string "If you have wonderful friends, there\n"
	.string "is no limit to how far you can go.$"

Ace_Trainer_BrennaIntro:
	.string "I’ve only been involved with Pokémon\n"
	.string "for a short time.\p"
	.string "I managed to get this far because\n"
	.string "skilled friends toughened me up!$"

Ace_Trainer_CatherineDefeat:
	.string "You’re the kind of person who can keep\n"
	.string "going forward even into the unknown.$"

Ace_Trainer_CatherinePostBattle:
	.string "I think, sometimes, one has to make\n"
	.string "mistakes to learn what is right.$"

Ace_Trainer_CatherineIntro:
	.string "What does it feel like, taking one step\n"
	.string "after another into darkness?$"

Ace_Trainer_CesarDefeat:
	.string "Wow...\n"
	.string "I’m in the mood to sing a lullaby...$"

Ace_Trainer_CesarPostBattle:
	.string "Your earnest enthusiasm...\n"
	.string "I guess that kinda makes you an ace.\p"
	.string "Maybe you’re a Trainer who has the\n"
	.string "potential to surpass aces!$"

Ace_Trainer_CesarIntro:
	.string "An ace has the knowledge and\n"
	.string "experience of battling at high levels.\p"
	.string "I’ll demonstrate what that means to\n"
	.string "a noob like you!$"

Ace_Trainer_ClariceDefeat:
	.string "You got way too much!$"

Ace_Trainer_ClaricePostBattle:
	.string "Well, I don’t have any advice for\n"
	.string "someone as tough as you!$"

Ace_Trainer_ClariceIntro:
	.string "Let me see what you got there, kid.\n"
	.string "I could give you some advice.$"

Ace_Trainer_DaltonDefeat:
	.string "Your heart burns as hot as mine!$"

Ace_Trainer_DaltonPostBattle:
	.string "The weather clears up sometimes.\n"
	.string "The view is breathtaking then.$"

Ace_Trainer_DaltonIntro:
	.string "This cold is but nothing compared\n"
	.string "to the fire that burns in my heart!$"

Ace_Trainer_DaltonRematch:
	.string "We’ll come at you with our hearts\n"
	.string "ablaze!$"

Ace_Trainer_DanaDefeat:
	.string "Your love of Pokémon really shows!$"

Ace_Trainer_DanaPostBattle:
	.string "I grew up together with Felix and\n"
	.string "my team, right from my childhood.\p"
	.string "All our memories, we’ve always shared\n"
	.string "them.$"

Ace_Trainer_DanaIntro:
	.string "You’re willing to battle?\n"
	.string "Let me see what you have?$"

Ace_Trainer_DanaRematch:
	.string "Oh, hi, we meet again.\p"
	.string "May I see what you’ve done with your\n"
	.string "Pokémon?$"

Ace_Trainer_DeannaDefeat:
	.string "I’ve found a tough adversary in\n"
	.string "you...$"

Ace_Trainer_DeannaPostBattle:
	.string "How much you believe in your\n"
	.string "Pokémon...\p"
	.string "That’s a critical factor in how a\n"
	.string "battle will turn out.$"

Ace_Trainer_DeannaIntro:
	.string "Worthy opponents... The search for\n"
	.string "them drives me to travel far.$"

Ace_Trainer_DeannaRematch:
	.string "We’ve faced many challengers since\n"
	.string "we met, but they were all weak...\p"
	.string "I relish the tough resistance that\n"
	.string "only you can provide!$"

Ace_Trainer_DennisDefeat:
	.string "You won and I lost, but the both of\n"
	.string "us gained something from this.$"

Ace_Trainer_DennisPostBattle:
	.string "In a Pokémon battle, it doesn’t\n"
	.string "matter how old or young you are.\p"
	.string "Your gender doesn’t matter, either.\n"
	.string "Nothing like that means anything!$"

Ace_Trainer_DennisIntro:
	.string "I’ll take on anyone!\n"
	.string "It can only make me stronger!$"

Ace_Trainer_DennisRematch:
	.string "I’ll battle against people who’ve\n"
	.string "beaten me again and again.\p"
	.string "By doing that, we both grow a little\n"
	.string "as Trainers.$"

Ace_Trainer_DestinyDefeat:
	.string "Your power is thrilling...\n"
	.string "I’m thrilled down to my toes!$"

Ace_Trainer_DestinyPostBattle:
	.string "I’m so glad that there are Pokémon!\p"
	.string "There isn’t much else that gives me\n"
	.string "the thrill that Pokémon do!$"

Ace_Trainer_DestinyIntro:
	.string "I’m not just looking for tough\n"
	.string "Trainers to battle.\p"
	.string "I’ve been battling here because\n"
	.string "I want to feel the rush!$"

Ace_Trainer_ErnestDefeat:
	.string "Haha!\n"
	.string "A total loss for me!$"

Ace_Trainer_ErnestPostBattle:
	.string "You seem to have an abundance of\n"
	.string "talent. It’s pretty amazing.$"

Ace_Trainer_ErnestIntro:
	.string "You seem to have a lot of confidence.\n"
	.string "Let’s see if it’s justified!$"

Ace_Trainer_ErnestRematch:
	.string "When I lost to you last time, I was\n"
	.string "just unlucky.$"

Ace_Trainer_FelixDefeat:
	.string "Did you enjoy the show?\n"
	.string "Super fabulous, wasn’t it?$"

Ace_Trainer_FelixPostBattle:
	.string "I’ll be happy to battle you again!\n"
	.string "Let’s battle again sometime, yeah?$"

Ace_Trainer_FelixIntro:
	.string "Welcome to my Pokémon show!$"

Ace_Trainer_FelixRematch:
	.string "Welcome to my new Pokémon show!$"

Ace_Trainer_GarrettDefeat:
	.string "Good job!\n"
	.string "That was an excellent battle.$"

Ace_Trainer_GarrettPostBattle:
	.string "If you don’t play for keeps, you’ll\n"
	.string "lose battles you should be dominating.$"

Ace_Trainer_GarrettIntro:
	.string "I always play for keeps!\n"
	.string "This isn’t practice!$"

Ace_Trainer_GarrettRematch:
	.string "When I lost to you last time, I was\n"
	.string "battling for keeps.\p"
	.string "But this time, I really mean it.\n"
	.string "This is seriously for keeps!$"

Ace_Trainer_GrahamDefeat:
	.string "It needs to be leveled more?!$"

Ace_Trainer_GrahamPostBattle:
	.string "My Pokémon...\p"
	.string "They’re the first friends I ever\n"
	.string "caught. They mean everything to me!$"

Ace_Trainer_GrahamIntro:
	.string "I took great pains raising my partners.\n"
	.string "I’ll show you how strong I made them!$"

Ace_Trainer_GrahamRematch:
	.string "...When I close my eyes, I can picture\n"
	.string "how we lost to you in vivid detail.\p"
	.string "But, I’ve raised them since then! I’ll\n"
	.string "throw their strength in your face!$"

Ace_Trainer_HenryDefeat:
	.string "That wasn’t how I planned the final\n"
	.string "chapter to go in my writing class...$"

Ace_Trainer_HenryPostBattle:
	.string "If you don’t give up, you can reach\n"
	.string "your goal.\p"
	.string "That perseverance is what’s important\n"
	.string "to Trainers. That’s in my book, too.$"

Ace_Trainer_HenryIntro:
	.string "Victory Road... Somehow, it feels as\n"
	.string "if my journey is now coming to an end.\p"
	.string "But, before the final chapter is\n"
	.string "written, I must pen your defeat!$"

Ace_Trainer_IsaiahDefeat:
	.string "You weren’t even fazed...$"

Ace_Trainer_IsaiahPostBattle:
	.string "I’ve battled countless Trainers\n"
	.string "and many more Pokémon still.\p"
	.string "My spirit has been hardened from all\n"
	.string "the battles I have fought.$"

Ace_Trainer_IsaiahIntro:
	.string "My willpower was shaped and tempered\n"
	.string "by howling blizzards.\p"
	.string "I’ll bring it to bear on you!$"

Ace_Trainer_JakeDefeat:
	.string "I’m burning with jealousy over your\n"
	.string "talent!$"

Ace_Trainer_JakePostBattle:
	.string "I think keeping up the effort to\n"
	.string "better yourself is a talent in itself.$"

Ace_Trainer_JakeIntro:
	.string "They call me an Ace Trainer.\p"
	.string "Allow me to demonstrate the talent\n"
	.string "that makes me so!$"

Ace_Trainer_JakeRematch:
	.string "Last time, you beat me before I had\n"
	.string "a chance to show you my skill.\p"
	.string "This time, I’ll shows you why they\n"
	.string "consider me an ace!$"

Ace_Trainer_JamieDefeat:
	.string "...Things don’t always work out\n"
	.string "according to my calculations...$"

Ace_Trainer_JamiePostBattle:
	.string "I had a lot of fun battling with\n"
	.string "you, though.\p"
	.string "I wonder if I can analyze the\n"
	.string "battle data properly?\p"
	.string "I could use a rematch to get\n"
	.string "some additional data.$"

Ace_Trainer_JamieIntro:
	.string "I constantly analyze Pokémon and\n"
	.string "various battles on my laptop.$"

Ace_Trainer_JamieRematch:
	.string "I analyzed our last battle on my\n"
	.string "laptop.$"

Ace_Trainer_JasminDefeat:
	.string "And another...\n"
	.string "A new memory was born.$"

Ace_Trainer_JasminPostBattle:
	.string "For me, space is where memories are\n"
	.string "made...$"

Ace_Trainer_JasminIntro:
	.string "Can you answer this for me?\n"
	.string "What is space?$"

Ace_Trainer_JonahDefeat:
	.string "You know, I would have really enjoyed\n"
	.string "a win there. Would’ve been real nice.$"

Ace_Trainer_JonahPostBattle:
	.string "This mine’s been abandoned, but\n"
	.string "now it’s home to many Pokémon.\p"
	.string "I guess everything finds a place\n"
	.string "to call home someday...$"

Ace_Trainer_JonahIntro:
	.string "If we were to battle, your Pokémon \n"
	.string "would become tougher.\p"
	.string "Likewise, my Pokémon would also\n"
	.string "become tougher.\p"
	.string "It’s all good.\n"
	.string "This calls for a battle!$"

Ace_Trainer_JoseDefeat:
	.string "Hmm. I like how you attack.$"

Ace_Trainer_JosePostBattle:
	.string "Pokémon and numbers...\n"
	.string "Who cares about that stuff?\p"
	.string "Winning is what’s important.\n"
	.string "Numbers aren’t everything.$"

Ace_Trainer_JoseIntro:
	.string "Have you any knowledge of levels\n"
	.string "or the stats of Pokémon? Well, I do!$"

Ace_Trainer_JoseRematch:
	.string "Pokémon battles aren’t decided by\n"
	.string "numbers.\p"
	.string "It’s the bond you share with your\n"
	.string "Pokémon that decides outcomes!$"

Ace_Trainer_KassandraDefeat:
	.string "Your dedication won out.$"

Ace_Trainer_KassandraPostBattle:
	.string "The Pokémon here must battle each\n"
	.string "other all the time.\p"
	.string "That must be why they are so strong\n"
	.string "in this area.$"

Ace_Trainer_KassandraIntro:
	.string "You’ve come all this way for Pokémon?\n"
	.string "You must be dedicated.$"

Ace_Trainer_KeenanDefeat:
	.string "I grow less certain still...$"

Ace_Trainer_KeenanPostBattle:
	.string "Perhaps there is no meaning to\n"
	.string "victory, but still I will battle!\p"
	.string "That is what makes me a Trainer!$"

Ace_Trainer_KeenanIntro:
	.string "What it means to win battles...\n"
	.string "That is what I seek.\p"
	.string "Teach me if you will!$"

Ace_Trainer_LauraDefeat:
	.string "Hunh?!$"

Ace_Trainer_LauraPostBattle:
	.string "Perhaps I should maybe change into\n"
	.string "a more comfy outfit...$"

Ace_Trainer_LauraIntro:
	.string "I’m fully kitted up and equipped!\n"
	.string "Anytime will be fine!$"

Ace_Trainer_LauraRematch:
	.string "I’m fully equipped again today!\n"
	.string "Anytime you’re ready will be fine!$"

Ace_Trainer_MariaDefeat:
	.string "Oh, yeah?\n"
	.string "Eat snowball, punk!$"

Ace_Trainer_MariaPostBattle:
	.string "You can make all the preparations in\n"
	.string "the world, but if it doesn’t work, it\p"
	.string "doesn’t work.$"

Ace_Trainer_MariaIntro:
	.string "To be ready to answer any call!\n"
	.string "To be ready to accept any challenge!\p"
	.string "That is the way of a Trainer!$"

Ace_Trainer_MariaRematch:
	.string "I got everything ready so we could\n"
	.string "have a rematch whenever you come.$"

Ace_Trainer_MariahDefeat:
	.string "So, that’s how you battled...?$"

Ace_Trainer_MariahPostBattle:
	.string "Once you emerge from Victory Road,\n"
	.string "the Pokémon League lies directly\p"
	.string "ahead...\p"
	.string "But many Trainers fail to ever find\n"
	.string "their way on Victory Road...$"

Ace_Trainer_MariahIntro:
	.string "Show me how you’ve battled to get\n"
	.string "here! Let’s do this!$"

Ace_Trainer_MayaDefeat:
	.string "You made me lose my confidence...$"

Ace_Trainer_MayaPostBattle:
	.string "I think about Pokémon all day long.\n"
	.string "I was confident, you know.$"

Ace_Trainer_MayaIntro:
	.string "I’m taking the Veilstone Gym\n"
	.string "challenge. But first...$"

Ace_Trainer_MayaRematch:
	.string "Oh, it’s you again!\p"
	.string "I’ve regained my confidence.\n"
	.string "Let’s have another battle!$"

Ace_Trainer_MeaganDefeat:
	.string "Yowch!$"

Ace_Trainer_MeaganPostBattle:
	.string "I heard that somewhere there’s\n"
	.string "someone who teaches Pokémon moves.$"

Ace_Trainer_MeaganIntro:
	.string "What sort of moves have you taught?\n"
	.string "That tells me how good you are!$"

Ace_Trainer_MeaganRematch:
	.string "Have you taught your team any new\n"
	.string "moves since last time?$"

Ace_Trainer_MicahDefeat:
	.string "Your Pokémon have a real peppy feel to\n"
	.string "them!$"

Ace_Trainer_MicahPostBattle:
	.string "Whether you’re talking to people or\n"
	.string "Pokémon, it’s important to always look\p"
	.string "them square in the eyes.$"

Ace_Trainer_MicahIntro:
	.string "When Trainers lock eyes...\p"
	.string "That’s right! It’s time to let\n"
	.string "their Pokémon go wild!$"

Ace_Trainer_MikaylaDefeat:
	.string "Wow, there are Pokémon that\n"
	.string "wonderful!$"

Ace_Trainer_MikaylaPostBattle:
	.string "There is always something to like\n"
	.string "about any Pokémon.\p"
	.string "It’s so hard to decide which ones\n"
	.string "I should raise.$"

Ace_Trainer_MikaylaIntro:
	.string "The world is huge, and there are\n"
	.string "so many different Pokémon!\p"
	.string "What kinds of Pokémon are with you?\n"
	.string "Please, I want to have a look!$"

Ace_Trainer_MikaylaRematch:
	.string "If I’m having trouble deciding,\n"
	.string "I go with my favorites!$"

Ace_Trainer_MoiraDefeat:
	.string "Hmm...$"

Ace_Trainer_MoiraPostBattle:
	.string "I feel invigorated from that battle,\n"
	.string "even though we lost.\p"
	.string "After all, we gave it everything we\n"
	.string "had.$"

Ace_Trainer_MoiraIntro:
	.string "Please don’t hold anything back.$"

Ace_Trainer_MoiraRematch:
	.string "Hello again! Please don’t hold\n"
	.string "anything back, just like before.$"

Ace_Trainer_MoniqueDefeat:
	.string "Aww...\n"
	.string "I’m out of useful items!$"

Ace_Trainer_MoniquePostBattle:
	.string "We came completely unprepared for\n"
	.string "this little adventure...$"

Ace_Trainer_MoniqueIntro:
	.string "We’re all good to go!\n"
	.string "We just have to battle now!$"

Ace_Trainer_NatashaDefeat:
	.string "But...\n"
	.string "I had a win streak going...$"

Ace_Trainer_NatashaPostBattle:
	.string "Train more at the Battle Tower...\n"
	.string "That’s what I’ll do.$"

Ace_Trainer_NatashaIntro:
	.string "I came here after winning my way\n"
	.string "through the Battle Tower!$"

Ace_Trainer_OliviaDefeat:
	.string "Whew...\n"
	.string "You’re overtrained for me.$"

Ace_Trainer_OliviaPostBattle:
	.string "Around these parts, perhaps because\n"
	.string "of all the snow, there are many\p"
	.string "folktales of hauntings...$"

Ace_Trainer_OliviaIntro:
	.string "Wh-what is it?\n"
	.string "P-Pokémon battle?!$"

Ace_Trainer_OliviaRematch:
	.string "This isn’t like last time. See how\n"
	.string "much I’ve trained since then!$"

Ace_Trainer_OmarDefeat:
	.string "You’re as tough as you look.$"

Ace_Trainer_OmarPostBattle:
	.string "One day, people will run to the other\n"
	.string "side of the road when I walk by ’em.\p"
	.string "It’s a goal of mine I’m working on.$"

Ace_Trainer_OmarIntro:
	.string "You... One look at you tells me\n"
	.string "you’re a real contender!$"

Ace_Trainer_QuinnDefeat:
	.string "My bunch got schooled, and how!$"

Ace_Trainer_QuinnPostBattle:
	.string "I fed my gang Protein, Carbos...\n"
	.string "You name it, I pumped ’em full of it.$"

Ace_Trainer_QuinnIntro:
	.string "I’ve pumped up my gang till they can’t\n"
	.string "get pumped no more.\p"
	.string "They’re going to school your Pokémon!$"

Ace_Trainer_QuinnRematch:
	.string "Hey! You’re that Trainer who schooled\n"
	.string "me and my Pokémon!\p"
	.string "OK, this time we’ll return the favor!\n"
	.string "We’ll be doing the schooling!$"

Ace_Trainer_RodolfoDefeat:
	.string "I see it now...$"

Ace_Trainer_RodolfoPostBattle:
	.string "Battling you was an eye-opener.\p"
	.string "I learned something very important\n"
	.string "in that short time.$"

Ace_Trainer_RodolfoIntro:
