Black_Belt_MilesPostBattle:
	.string "I’ve made it this far in life using the\n"
	.string "karate I learned on the Internet!$"

Black_Belt_MilesIntro:
	.string "My Pokémon knows karate!\n"
	.string "I’m warning you, it’s a tough one!$"

Black_Belt_NathanielDefeat:
	.string "I should be lighter by the amount of\n"
	.string "sweat I just shed!$"

Black_Belt_NathanielPostBattle:
	.string "It’s time for another workout.\n"
	.string "The more I sweat, the tougher I get!$"

Black_Belt_NathanielIntro:
	.string "Every drop of sweat I shed makes\n"
	.string "me that much stronger!$"

