	.string "Oh, gosh, this is bad! I think I’m\n"
	.string "losing feeling all over my body!$"

Black_Belt_PhilipIntro:
	.string "I can withstand this cold. That means\n"
	.string "I can take any kind of attack!$"

Black_Belt_PhilipRematch:
	.string "Oh? I’ve seen your face before.\n"
	.string "What say we battle?$"

Black_Belt_RafaelDefeat:
	.string "We came up short, but not by much.$"

Black_Belt_RafaelPostBattle:
	.string "I’ll have to redo my training, though.\n"
	.string "Maylene’s gonna trample me again...$"

Black_Belt_RafaelIntro:
	.string "We’re the Karate Quads!\p"
	.string "I will strike a blow for hope with my\n"
	.string "fist! Hiyah, hoooooooooooooope!$"

Black_Belt_RayDefeat:
	.string "We weren’t up to the task!$"

Black_Belt_RayPostBattle:
	.string "Even though my team could break\n"
	.string "bricks and shatter boulders, they\p"
	.string "failed to dent your spirits!$"

Black_Belt_RayIntro:
	.string "My Pokémon can destroy anything.\n"
	.string "And you think you can win?!$"

