	.string "I never gave up, but still I failed to\n"
	.string "win...$"

Black_Belt_RickyPostBattle:
	.string "If you give up, well, that’s when\n"
	.string "everything ends for you!$"

Black_Belt_RickyIntro:
	.string "Steel represents an unbending spirit!\p"
	.string "If one refuses to accept defeat,\n"
	.string "the path to victory reveals itself!$"

Black_Belt_SeanDefeat:
	.string "I don’t get why we can’t win.$"

Black_Belt_SeanPostBattle:
	.string "I don’t reminisce over yesterday.\n"
	.string "I don’t think about tomorrow.\p"
	.string "I only live today to the fullest.\n"
	.string "That’s my policy!$"

Black_Belt_SeanIntro:
	.string "Hah! Hah!\n"
	.string "I’m psyched for this! Here goes!$"

Black_Belt_SeanRematch:
	.string "Hiyah! Hiyah! Hiyah! Hiyah!\n"
	.string "This time, I’m properly psyched!$"

Black_Belt_WillieDefeat:
	.string "Wrroar!\n"
	.string "Judo chop defeated!$"

Black_Belt_WilliePostBattle:
	.string "I’ll forget that we lost!\p"
	.string "...Wait, if I did that, we’d never\n"
	.string "learn from our mistakes...$"

Black_Belt_WillieIntro:
	.string "Judo chop!\n"
	.string "Pokémon battle!$"

Breeder_AlbertDefeat:
	.string "Good stuff! Your Pokémon are in\n"
	.string "impeccable condition.$"

Breeder_AlbertPostBattle:
	.string "It’s obvious you raise your Pokémon\n"
	.string "with a lot of love.$"

Breeder_AlbertIntro:
	.string "Let me see how much you’ve raised\n"
	.string "your Pokémon.$"

Breeder_AlbertRematch:
	.string "I’ve raised my Pokémon since we met.\n"
	.string "How much have you raised yours?$"

Breeder_AmberDefeat:
	.string "It’s all right!\n"
	.string "I’m still a rookie!$"

Breeder_AmberPostBattle:
	.string "The best way to raise Pokémon?\p"
	.string "...Hmm, when it comes right down to it,\n"
	.string "isn’t it all about love?$"

Breeder_AmberIntro:
	.string "I’m a rookie breeder, but I’ll do\n"
	.string "my very best!$"

Breeder_AmberRematch:
	.string "I can’t be a rookie forever.\n"
	.string "I’ve learned a lot since we last met.$"

Breeder_JenniferDefeat:
	.string "Giggle...\n"
	.string "They’re raised with a lot of care!$"

Breeder_JenniferPostBattle:
	.string "Raise your Pokémon with lots of love,\n"
	.string "and they’ll bond closely with you.$"

Breeder_JenniferIntro:
	.string "Please, let me battle the Pokémon\n"
	.string "you’ve raised!$"

Breeder_JenniferRematch:
	.string "I don’t want to ever battle with\n"
	.string "people who don’t treat Pokémon nice!\p"
	.string "But I know you treat yours kindly.\n"
	.string "I’ll battle you anytime!$"

Breeder_KahlilDefeat:
	.string "Hey, hey, did you take a good look?$"

Breeder_KahlilPostBattle:
	.string "The Veilstone Department Store is\n"
	.string "pretty impressive!\p"
	.string "Did you know they even sell Poffins?$"

Breeder_KahlilIntro:
	.string "Hey, check this out! Look at the\n"
	.string "luster of my Pokémon’s fur!$"

Breeder_KahlilRematch:
	.string "I brushed my party a lot.\n"
	.string "So we’d be ready for a rematch!$"

Breeder_KayleeDefeat:
	.string "You know, I had confidence before\n"
	.string "heading into this.$"

Buck_BattlegroundDefeat:
	.string "Heeheehee!\n"
	.string "So hot, you!$"

Bug_Catcher_BrandonDefeat:
