	.string "the charms of bug Pokémon this way!$"

Bug_Catcher_BrandonPostBattle:
	.string "Bug Pokémon grow quickly, and they do\n"
	.string "stuff like poison and paralyze, and\p"
	.string "they’re cute and yet cool.\p"
	.string "You gotta believe me. They’re good!$"

Bug_Catcher_BrandonIntro:
	.string "Hey, hey, let me show off my bug\n"
	.string "Pokémon!$"

Bug_Catcher_BrandonRematch:
	.string "So, listen. Tell me you’ve grown to\n"
	.string "like bug Pokémon since we last met.$"

Bug_Catcher_DonaldDefeat:
	.string "Awawawawah...$"

Bug_Catcher_DonaldPostBattle:
	.string "I thought it was a rare Pokémon, but\n"
	.string "it turned out to be just a Trainer!$"

Bug_Catcher_DonaldIntro:
	.string "My senses tingle...\n"
	.string "I’ve spotted a rare Pokémon!$"

Bug_Catcher_JackDefeat:
	.string "Don’t ignore bug Pokémon!\n"
	.string "That really bugs me!$"

Bug_Catcher_JackPostBattle:
	.string "It would seem that coolness alone\n"
	.string "doesn’t add up to any wins...$"

Bug_Catcher_JackIntro:
	.string "What’s cool, you might ask? No?\n"
	.string "I’ll tell you anyway: bug Pokémon!$"

Bug_Catcher_PhillipDefeat:
	.string "Whoooh...$"

Bug_Catcher_PhillipPostBattle:
	.string "There’s a Pokémon ability named Swarm.$"

Bug_Catcher_PhillipIntro:
	.string "Here comes the swarm!$"

Cameraman_DarrylDefeat:
	.string "That’s quite the demonstration.$"

Cameraman_TevinDefeat:
	.string "My camera’s too heavy.\n"
	.string "I couldn’t battle effectively...$"

Cameraman_Tevin_UnusedDefeat:
	.string "My camera’s too heavy.\n"
	.string "I couldn’t battle effectively...$"

Cameraman_Tevin_UnusedPostBattle:
	.string "The lively expressions on you and\n"
	.string "your Pokémon’s faces...\p"
	.string "It sure makes for some great TV!$"

Cameraman_Tevin_UnusedIntro:
	.string "I’ve spotted a charismatic Trainer!\n"
	.string "We just might have a scoop here!$"

Camper_AnthonyDefeat:
	.string "Oh...\n"
	.string "We lost...$"

Camper_AnthonyPostBattle:
	.string "Dig for Fossils in the Underground.\p"
	.string "The mining museum might be able to\n"
	.string "bring back the ancient Pokémon!$"

Camper_AnthonyIntro:
	.string "Go for it, my Pokémon!\n"
	.string "I’ll do my best, too!$"

Camper_AnthonyRematch:
	.string "Go for it, my Pokémon!\n"
	.string "I’ll do more than my best this time!$"

Camper_DiegoDefeat:
	.string "You didn’t really have to win!\n"
	.string "I’m not going to guide you now!$"

Camper_DiegoPostBattle:
	.string "I’m not lost, I tell you!\n"
	.string "I’m camping! That’s my story!$"

Camper_DiegoIntro:
	.string "Humph! You’re lost, aren’t you?\n"
	.string "I’ll guide you if you can beat me.$"

Camper_DrewDefeat:
	.string "Yeah, whatever.\n"
	.string "You can battle, too...$"

Camper_DrewPostBattle:
	.string "I’m gonna visit new places and find\n"
	.string "new Pokémon so I’ll be a know-it-all!$"

Camper_DrewIntro:
	.string "I’ve been to all sorts of places.\n"
	.string "That means I know tons of things!$"

