	.string "I should’ve just stuck to\n"
	.string "camping out here...$"

Camper_LawrencePostBattle:
	.string "When I’m with my Pokémon, I can camp\n"
	.string "just about anywhere I want!$"

Camper_LawrenceIntro:
	.string "Yeah, I like to camp! So what?\n"
	.string "Let’s battle!$"

