	.string "Lost?\n"
	.string "There’s nothing lost about this kid!$"

Camper_ParkerPostBattle:
	.string "I got separated from my friends...\p"
	.string "I’ve got my Pokémon with me, so I’m\n"
	.string "OK, but...$"

Camper_ParkerIntro:
	.string "Huh? Are you lost too?\n"
	.string "No? It doesn’t matter.\p"
	.string "Let’s have a quick Pokémon battle!$"

Camper_ZackaryDefeat:
	.string "Wawawaah!\n"
	.string "I’m out of Pokémon that can battle!$"

Camper_ZackaryPostBattle:
	.string "Camping with Pokémon!\n"
	.string "Do you have any idea how fun that is?$"

Camper_ZackaryIntro:
	.string "It’s a long way between Floaroma\n"
	.string "and Eterna City. So, let’s battle!$"

Camper_ZackaryRematch:
	.string "While I was enjoying camping, my\n"
	.string "Pokémon got all big and buffed up!$"

Castle_Valet_Darach_DummyDefeat:
	.string "My Pokémon can’t be faulted with\n"
	.string "anything.\p"
	.string "Your brilliance carried the day.$"

Champion_CynthiaDefeat:
	.string "...Just a few minutes ago, you were\n"
	.string "the most powerful challenger.\p"
	.string "And just now, you became the most\n"
	.string "powerful of all the Trainers.\p"
	.string "You are now our newest Champion!$"

Cheryl_BattlegroundDefeat:
	.string "Striking the right balance of offense\n"
	.string "and defense... It’s not easy to do.$"

Clown_LeeDefeat:
	.string "Oh, no, no, no!\n"
	.string "Mwahahah?$"

Clown_Lee_UnusedDefeat:
	.string "Oh, no, no, no!\n"
	.string "Mwahahah?$"

Clown_Lee_UnusedPostBattle:
	.string "A clown’s makeup is a face that’s\n"
	.string "crying while laughing. Mwahahah!\p"
	.string "It defines what we do!$"

Clown_Lee_UnusedIntro:
	.string "Are we all ready to have some fun?\n"
	.string "I sure am! Aren’t you having fun?!\p"
	.string "Let’s make it fun! OK?! Mwahahah!$"

Collector_BradyDefeat:
	.string "Your Pokédex fills me with such envy,\n"
	.string "envy, envy...$"

Collector_BradyPostBattle:
	.string "There’s all kinds of Trainers with all\n"
	.string "sorts of Pokémon with them.\p"
	.string "The more you battle, the more your\n"
	.string "Pokédex is filled!$"

