	.string "What’s that?!\p"
	.string "You say you have a Pokédex?\n"
	.string "An authentic one!$"

Collector_BradyRematch:
	.string "Ooh, thank you!\p"
	.string "You came back to show me your Pokédex\n"
	.string "because I don’t have one!$"

