	.string "Oh, what have we here?\n"
	.string "That’s a Pokédex!\p"
	.string "It records Pokémon data upon\n"
	.string "sight? I’ve never seen one before!\p"
	.string "I heard you can move the sun or\n"
	.string "moon icon to check the Pokémon\p"
	.string "habitat map by time of day!$"

Collector_DeanIntro:
	.string "I’m proud of my Pokémon!\n"
	.string "Here, I’ll show you why!$"

