	.string "You ought to be proud of it!$"

Collector_DouglasPostBattle:
	.string "I take pride in having Pokémon that\n"
	.string "others don’t.\p"
	.string "Oh, I’m also proud about winning second\n"
	.string "prize in one of Jubilife TV’s drawings.$"

Collector_DouglasIntro:
	.string "For the sake of my collection, I\n"
	.string "take on people I know I can’t beat.\p"
	.string "That’s what a Collector does.$"

Collector_DouglasRematch:
	.string "For the sake of my collection, I\n"
	.string "keep battling people I can’t beat.\p"
	.string "That’s what a Collector does.$"

Collector_EdwinDefeat:
	.string "What’ve you done to my Pokémon?!\p"
	.string "It took me forever to catch it using\n"
	.string "Honey!$"

Collector_EdwinPostBattle:
	.string "I went through a lot of bother to catch\n"
	.string "my Pokémon.\p"
	.string "But since I’ve not raised it, it’s\n"
	.string "as weak as when I caught it.$"

Collector_EdwinIntro:
	.string "I’m a Collector, and I love Honey!$"

Collector_EugeneDefeat:
	.string "I don’t care if I lose.\n"
	.string "I’m still a happy guy.$"

Collector_FernandoDefeat:
	.string "Knowledge alone isn’t everything,\n"
	.string "you know...$"

Collector_FernandoPostBattle:
	.string "I’m more knowledgeable than anyone\n"
	.string "else!\p"
	.string "I have a rare Pokémon!\p"
	.string "But, I’m weak at battling...\n"
	.string "That’s a Pokémon Collector for you...$"

Collector_FernandoIntro:
	.string "We were having a heated discussion\n"
	.string "over Pokémon the way Collectors do.$"

Collector_IvanDefeat:
	.string "You’re one enthusiastic Trainer.$"

