	.string "Pal Park, huh? I wonder what kinds\n"
	.string "of Pokémon you can see there?$"

Collector_IvanIntro:
	.string "Are you going to the Pal Park, too?\p"
	.string "For you, I’m willing to show off my\n"
	.string "prized Pokémon!$"

Collector_IvanRematch:
	.string "Pal Park, huh? I wonder what kinds\n"
	.string "of Pokémon you can see there?$"

Collector_JamalDefeat:
	.string "But they’re rare Pokémon!$"

Collector_JamalPostBattle:
	.string "If you’re trying to find the Pokémon\n"
	.string "you want, you need to go everywhere!\p"
	.string "Not just east and west, either.\n"
	.string "South and north are important, too!$"

Collector_JamalIntro:
	.string "To find my favorite Pokémon, I’ll go\n"
	.string "east, west, or any which way!$"

Collector_JamalRematch:
	.string "For my favorite Pokémon, I’ll go\n"
	.string "east, west, or any which way!\p"
	.string "...Saying that, I’ve been wandering\n"
	.string "around here all this time.$"

Collector_TerryDefeat:
	.string "You didn’t have a single Pokémon\n"
	.string "I wanted... You’re no Collector!$"

Collector_TerryPostBattle:
	.string "I’m very picky, so I want to collect\n"
	.string "every Pokémon without anyone’s help.\p"
	.string "...I do have friends, though.\n"
	.string "No, seriously! I do!$"

Collector_TerryIntro:
	.string "You look like you might just have\n"
	.string "the Pokémon I’ve been looking for!$"

Commander_Jupiter_Spear_PillarDefeat:
	.string "Humph! You’ve toughened up.\n"
	.string "But you’re no match for our boss.$"

Commander_Jupiter_Stark_MountainDefeat:
	.string "Humph! Quit flaunting your toughness!\n"
	.string "It’s not cute in the least!$"

Commander_Jupiter_Team_Galactic_Eterna_BuildingDefeat:
	.string "Losing to some child...\n"
	.string "Being careless cost me too much.$"

Commander_Mars_Lake_VerityDefeat:
	.string "...!\n"
	.string "Again and again...$"

Commander_Mars_Spear_PillarDefeat:
	.string "Sheesh... I should have done the\n"
	.string "fighting myself.$"

Commander_Mars_Stark_MountainDefeat:
	.string "What’s with you?!\n"
	.string "Do you have a vendetta against me?!$"

Commander_Mars_Valley_WindworksDefeat:
	.string "This can’t be?! I lost?!\n"
	.string "You...you uppity brat!$"

Commander_Saturn_Galactic_HqDefeat:
	.string "You’re tough, kid!\n"
	.string "But, I still pity the likes of you.$"

Commander_Saturn_Valor_CavernDefeat:
	.string "...You, my friend, are tough!\n"
	.string "I can see why you defy us so...$"

Cowgirl_ShelleyDefeat:
	.string "Fancy folks like you have fancy\n"
	.string "Pokémon too, it looks like.$"

Cowgirl_ShelleyPostBattle:
	.string "While working the ranch, I get to raise\n"
	.string "my Pokémon, too.\p"
	.string "I’d say it’s the best of both worlds!$"

Cowgirl_ShelleyIntro:
	.string "Say, honey, where’d you come from?\n"
	.string "What kinds of Pokémon are you with?$"

Cowgirl_ShelleyRematch:
	.string "Oh, howdy! Come visiting again?\n"
	.string "What kinds of Pokémon’d you bring?$"

Cyclist_AxelDefeat:
	.string "Hey, not bad, you!$"

Cyclist_AxelPostBattle:
	.string "This Cycling Road is one fine place--\n"
	.string "great bikes, superb Pokémon,\p"
	.string "and awesome Trainers all around!$"

Cyclist_AxelIntro:
	.string "Yo! Cycling and Pokémon!\n"
	.string "Which do you prefer?$"

Cyclist_AxelRematch:
	.string "I’m sure I’ve seen your face before.\n"
	.string "Did we maybe battle?$"

Cyclist_JamesDefeat:
	.string "Despite all the effort, I’m just spinning\n"
	.string "my wheels...\p"
	.string "It’s always that way with me!$"

Cyclist_JamesPostBattle:
	.string "I might try racing through Cycling\n"
	.string "Road in one long shot.$"

Cyclist_JamesIntro:
	.string "Ding-ding! Watch out, you!\n"
	.string "Or, did you want to battle?$"

Cyclist_JamesRematch:
	.string "There you are!\p"
	.string "I’ve been riding in this spot so I’d\n"
	.string "get a rematch with you!$"

Cyclist_JohnDefeat:
	.string "Crash! Tinkle...$"

Cyclist_JohnPostBattle:
	.string "The 3-speed makes for easy turning,\n"
	.string "and the 4-speed’s for going fast.\p"
	.string "I love them both!$"

Cyclist_JohnIntro:
	.string "That Bike you’ve got there...it’s the\n"
	.string "type that can change gears!\p"
	.string "You gotta love that!\n"
	.string "Sure, I’ll give you a battle!$"

Cyclist_JohnRematch:
	.string "Is your bicycle geared to 3-speed now?\n"
	.string "Or do you have it set to 4-speed?$"

Cyclist_KaylaDefeat:
	.string "Kerrrash!$"

Cyclist_KaylaPostBattle:
	.string "Aww!\n"
	.string "Why did you beat me?!\p"
	.string "I hope you get so lost in Wayward Cave\n"
	.string "you cry! Boo-hoo-hoo!$"

Cyclist_KaylaIntro:
	.string "If you beat me, you can count on\n"
	.string "something rotten coming your way!$"

Cyclist_KaylaRematch:
	.string "I had to get my revenge on you.\p"
	.string "I trained my Pokémon while lost and\p"
	.string "wandering in the Wayward Cave!$"

Cyclist_MeganDefeat:
	.string "Whew!\n"
	.string "You worked us over.$"

Cyclist_MeganPostBattle:
	.string "I like spinning the pedals backward\n"
	.string "while sailing downhill.$"

Cyclist_MeganIntro:
	.string "Cycling feels great!\p"
	.string "It will feel even better when I beat\n"
	.string "you in a battle!$"

Cyclist_MeganRematch:
	.string "It feels great on my Bike!\p"
	.string "I’m already sweaty, so let’s have a\n"
	.string "rematch!$"

Cyclist_NicoleDefeat:
	.string "Oh, geez...\n"
	.string "I seem to have fallen off my Bike.$"

Cyclist_NicolePostBattle:
	.string "I should have challenged you to a race,\n"
	.string "not a battle!$"

Cyclist_NicoleIntro:
	.string "The both of us are on Bikes, and we\n"
	.string "both have Pokémon!\p"
	.string "I can’t let you get the better of me!$"

Cyclist_NicoleRematch:
	.string "I hate knowing you’ve beaten me.\n"
	.string "This time, I’m going to win!$"

Cyclist_RachelDefeat:
	.string "You’re a speedy technician!$"

Cyclist_RachelPostBattle:
	.string "I enjoy the scenery.\p"
	.string "Don’t you think the area below\n"
	.string "Cycling Road looks nice?$"

Cyclist_RachelIntro:
	.string "Some people compete over speed, and\n"
	.string "some compete over technique.\p"
	.string "Which kind are you?$"

Cyclist_RachelRematch:
	.string "I polished up both my speed and\n"
	.string "techniques. Can you beat me now?$"

Cyclist_RyanDefeat:
	.string "Gasp... Gasp... Gasp...$"

Cyclist_RyanPostBattle:
	.string "My Pokémon and I are plumb worn out.\n"
	.string "We should be getting home to rest...$"

Cyclist_RyanIntro:
	.string "A bike will carry you a long way.\p"
	.string "The only thing that limits you is your\n"
	.string "own endurance!$"

Cyclist_RyanRematch:
	.string "We took a recuperative rest.\n"
	.string "We’re not losing this time!$"

Dragon_Tamer_ClintonDefeat:
	.string "That’s why I like it here; I get to\n"
